BARD COMMAND LADDER

Use help <command> for exact syntax. Use bcmds for a live list based on your
current guild level.

Probationer - guild level 1

  bard             Guild chat line.
  bemotes          List Bard emotes.
  bmon             Toggle the Bard performance monitor.
  bpatterns        Show hidden harmonies and pivots you have discovered.
  bscore           Show Bard stats and Performance.
  fix lute         Retune and restore your Bardic lute anywhere.
  instrument       Select an alternate Bard instrument.
  legend           Read information about items.
  lore             Rate a monster relative to yourself.
  play lute        Play a single note for others nearby.
  pulsebeat        Start a Rhythm song field for nearby allies.

Fochlucan - guild level 2

  emberaria        Start a Melody song field around you.
  silververse      Start a Melody song field that mends allies.
  playdead         Trick people into thinking you are a corpse.
  scroll           Create a scroll.

Rhymer - guild level 3

  echochord        Start a Harmony song field around you.
  perform          People toss coins into your hat.

MacFuirmidh - guild level 4

  dirgeash         Start a Dissonance song that unsettles enemies.
  drunk            You heal faster when drunk.
  Sing             Attract a follower to help you.

Doss - guild level 5

  defame           Spread nasty rumours about people.
  fame             Give someone a good reputation.

Lyrist - guild level 6

  ashlullaby       Start a Dissonance song that mesmerizes enemies.
  soothe           Melody song that calms combat in a room.

Canaith - guild level 7

  hero             Harmony role song for heroic combat.
  lite             Cast a spell to create a light.
  villain          Dissonance role song for villainous combat.

Troubador - guild level 8

  act              Pretend to be someone else.
  brestore         Undo the effects of a defaming.
  mirrorrefrain    Chimes song that disrupts enemy timing.
  whispercanticle  Flute song that clouds enemy focus.

Sonateer - guild level 9

  compose          Write songs for the fiddler to play.

Cli - guild level 10

  :                Bard emoter.
  apexchord        Crescendo song for high Performance.
  echoburst        Finale that bursts active song fields.
  specialize       Choose or view your Bard archetype.
  vent             Ventriloquism.

Anstruth - guild level 11

  muse             Harmony song field that inspires allies.

Muse - guild level 12

  battlefieldsilence  Finale that disrupts nearby enemies.
  brew             Make your own white lightning.
  study            Read a target's bardic emotional resonance.

Racaraide - guild level 13

  otto             Dissonance song that forces a target to dance.

Ollamh - guild level 14

  rally            Harmony song that lends courage to allies.
  ssing            Create a singing sword.

Magna Alumnae - guild level 15

  Wail             Finale that releases a banshee wail.
